:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34958,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/01\/17\/janazah-many-believers\/","url_meta":{"origin":3347,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Janazah: Virtue of many believers performing funeral prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 17, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is prayed over by a hundred Muslims at his funeral, he will be forgiven.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1488 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43679,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/14\/prophet-always-with-abu-bakr-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":3347,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: The Prophet always with Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 14, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Umar was placed upon his bier as the people surrounded him, supplicated for him, and performed the funeral prayer over him before he was taken away. I was there, and not